<typeStatus id="7F45881DFFA5603AFA21FC7867969457" box="[305,408,1022,1048]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">lectotype</typeStatus>
designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="C46F4B4EFFA5603AF959FC7865369456" author="Lonsing, A." box="[585,824,1022,1049]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" pagination="139 - 166" refId="ref119026" refString="Lonsing, A. (1939) XXIII. (LX.) Uber einjahrige europaische Cerastium - Arten aus der Verwandtschaft der Gruppen &quot; Ciliatopetala &quot; Fenzl und &quot; Cryptodon &quot; Pax. Repertorium specierum novarum regni vegetabilis 46: 139 - 166." type="journal article" year="1939">Lonsing (1939: 161)</bibRefCitation>
. Lonsing had seen both the vouchers in the WU main collection and the WU-Halácsy-Graec. (which during this period were stored at the university), thus it remains unclear to which of the duplicates he refers. We here designate the voucher in the herbarium WU-Halácsy-Graec. (WU 0074338) as second-step 
<typeStatus id="7F45881DFFA5603AFAB4FBEC640594CB" box="[420,523,1130,1156]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">lectotype</typeStatus>
according to Art. 9.17 (
<bibRefCitation id="C46F4B4EFFA5603AF805FBEC65FF94CB" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[789,1009,1130,1156]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58" refId="ref126469" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (Eds.) (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Koeltz Botanical Books, Glashutten. [Regnum Vegetabile 159] Available from: https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / Code. 2018 (accessed 20 September 2019)" type="journal volume" year="2018">
